url: "https://github.com/creator35lwb-web/godelai"
abstract: "GodelAI is an open-source continual learning framework built on the C-S-P (Compression → State → Propagation) philosophy. It implements a Two-Layer Architecture: (1) GodelReplay — a training-time system combining Avalanche Replay with GodelPlugin (Fisher-scaled EWC-DR) for catastrophic forgetting reduction, validated on PermutedMNIST (10 tasks, mem=200 sweet spot: +4.1% forgetting reduction over Replay-only); and (2) GodelAI-Lite — an inference-time memory system using MemPalace, MACP, and GIFP, validated at +31.2% overall performance on Gemma 4. The C-S-P framework maps identically across both layers: Compression (Fisher Information / extract_facts), State (EWC-DR penalty / godelai_memory.json), and Propagation (replay buffer / portable JSON)."
keywords:
